(14) Feasibility of developing a business park or similar economic use.
(15) Compatibility with existing zoning and land use plans.
(16) Infrastructure requirements, including transportation and utilities.
(17) Potential roles of state and local entities in land assembly and redevelopment.
(18) Feasibility of utilizing a public redevelopment authority or similar structure.
(19) Phased approaches prioritizing voluntary acquisition and adjudicated properties.
(20) Assessment of potential impacts on nearby residents.
(21) Recommendations to ensure that any proposed actions do not displace residents
of occupied residential properties.
(22) Strategies for community engagement and transparency.
